-- Brasil Brokers, HSBC Sign 5-Year Partnership for Brazil Real-Estate Loans
-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 2010-10-15T07:08:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/brasil-brokers-hsbc-sign-5-year-partnership-for-brazil-real-estate-loans.html
Brasil Brokers Participacoes SA  and
HSBC Bank Brasil SA signed a five-year partnership to promote
and offer real-estate loans in the South American country.  Brasil Brokers will receive commission from HSBC for each
loan made during the  partnership , which can be extended for a
further five years, the Brazilian real-estate company said in a
regulatory filing today. HSBC will pay commission in advanced
installments to Brasil Brokers.  Brasil Brokers said it estimates total commission of 156
million reais in the first five years and 425 million reais in
10 years, according to the filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
